Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:25.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The infirmary?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:35.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you went through a lot didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you survived as a leader with that performance of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:45.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:47.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadows are all gone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:52.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be anything more in your way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:55.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:57.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:00.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:01.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:05.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:07.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:08.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:13.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just guessing, but maybe Yuri got over her troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:18.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:19.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.61,0:01:22.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:25.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll make her talk with my hypno—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:27.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she got so angry must mean we're right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:35.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a joke if my problems could be solved so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, my hypnotism will—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:42.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I got over them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:44.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:45.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she admitted it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:52.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a bully, Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:54.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just not honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:56.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:02:00.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm kind of happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:01.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That you called me Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:05.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:08.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make us friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:10.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:12.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess our preparations didn't go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:16.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:17.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:19.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:22.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade said there was something she wanted to do before the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:24.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she hasn't done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:26.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They all left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:35.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to everyone helping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely had a tough time though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was but light work for God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:48.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've realized that at the end of the day, everyone had fun living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's thanks to you, Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Takamatsu managed to leave too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He somehow regained his senses even after becoming an NPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say there was no way to return once you became an NPC?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:09.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that it was set up so that strong enough feelings could bring you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that song again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:19.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were humming it earlier when we were working too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The last song Iwasawa sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"My Song".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that was broadcast over the entire school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:34.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good song, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The gymnasium?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:52.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it together, and the letters were written by Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan hasn't graduated before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking it might be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:04.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you enjoyed writing the banner though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the girls cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why girls are just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we start then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why else did you change into uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought maybe I'll really vanish, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I'm prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, and you called yourself a leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:25.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:30.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually seem to be a lot less leader{\fnNyala}-{\fn}like after everyone vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,R{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:34.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely something different about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of more girl{\fnNyala}-{\fn}like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I be happy about that?{FOTC: As a character, you should absolutely hate it. It ruins the awesomeness completely.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:49.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After the fighting finished, you really became quite the innocent little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite a cute side, Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri's quite funny, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We hereby begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:11.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Graduation Ceremony for those who fought in the Afterlife Battlefront will be held now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with the chorus of our battle anthem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle anthem? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Afterlife Battlefront's anthem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a replacement for a school anthem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember having anyone compose something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:26.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also Kanade's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:28.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you aren't even a Battlefront member to start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:32.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the melody?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All school anthems sound pretty much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine if we just sing whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:41.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:48.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From the dead world in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:52.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We bring you a familiar number
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:56.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat some before you die
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:01.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mapo tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:05.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, mapo tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:10.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mapo tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this song?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone should have checked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:15.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually sang this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:18.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kanade did her best to write it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:26.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? She put "a familiar number" right here... {need better TL, see above}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling Kanade put a lot of effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What part?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:35.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From the start till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduating class diploma presentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:48.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have those?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, mostly Kanade's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have a Principal to present them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:06.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I lost at rock{\fnNyala}-{\fn}paper{\fnNyala}-{\fn}scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:07.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I always getting stuck with these jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That role suits you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduating class diploma presentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Tachibana Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:25.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Nakamura Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:55.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:16.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:20.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Naoi Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your services.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi Yuzuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:42.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:44.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:49.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here, thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Address from the representative of the graduating class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:22.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, we've been through quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:27.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The first person I met in this school was Nakamura Yuri{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing she told me was that I was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:41.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she said that the people living here in the afterlife were unable to accept their deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:43.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and that they were rebelling against God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I also fought alongside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:53.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But after I regained my memories, I was able to accept my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those memories were irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:02.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted everyone to experience that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They had rebelled for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:09.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was truly a difficult task.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:16.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But they were able to help one another, and believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:24.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This Battlefront, founded by Nakamura Yuri, was a group that was capable of such.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:31.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning that strength into courage, they began to accept their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:38.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, they all faced forward and departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the five of us remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...will graduate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we forget the faces of our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:56.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we will never forget the bonds that were carved into our souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly blessed to have been able to spend this time with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:03.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Representative of the graduating class, Otonashi Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rendition of "Aogeba Toutoshi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:30.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As we look with reverence upon our debt to you, teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:43.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in this garden of learning, how quickly these few years have passed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:56.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As we think upon them, these years and months have flown by all too soon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:12:05.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let us part
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were late, scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:12.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's you who was way too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:17.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely different when you're talking to Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:25.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ceremony closure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:48.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We bring the Afterlife Battlefront graduation ceremony to an end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduates, dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see any womanly tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:00.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my leave first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look who's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:17.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't met you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:22.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,would never have found peace... {missing line, demo ???}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I... {timing check and suggest rewording to the audio}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:32.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:34.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:38.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, who wants to cry next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:54.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I fought you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:01.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why I couldn't be your friend sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the eldest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:13.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was always looking after my sisters and brother for my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:18.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have showed you so many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:23.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you look like you don't get out much, so I was really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:26.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We could have done so many things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We could have had so much fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:34.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we had more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:36.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:38.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,it's time to part...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:51.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:06.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:18.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's my turn now, if we go in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go off and leave Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:27.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:30.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, this wouldn't have been possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and we wouldn't have been able to finish things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:39.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:46.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, I wasn't supposed to have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:52.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to find fulfillment in life at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:56.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I lost that memory, and mistakenly wandered into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:02.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After remembering that, I knew what it was like to lead a full life even though I was in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a special person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:15.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So like I said, it was just chance that I was able to help everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:16.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:19.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's enough talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find Yui, say hi to her for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved up plenty of luck, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:31.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:52.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So... what did you think of the graduation ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the last part is sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the start of a journey though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:06.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's begun a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:21.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to feel the wind a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:37.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanade...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of just realized it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:47.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:55.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are others like Yuri and Hinata and the rest, who couldn't find peace in life and will find there way here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:06.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And they might end up staying here, like Yuri, and be sad and keep suffering, and keep resisting life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:14.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,if we stay here, we can teach them, like we did this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:19.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,about how good it is to be alive, and help them graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:24.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I came here to play that role...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,won't you stay with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:35.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stayed here, I wouldn't be lonely, even in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:40.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have said it before, but I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to walk forward together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:50.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:55.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:03.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:13.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I tell you my feelings, I'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:15.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:21.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I came here to say thank you to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:31.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to stay alive because of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:39.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, your heart is beating in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:48.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My one regret was being unable to say thank you to the person who saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:55.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you so badly that I got lost and wandered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:59.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized it the first time I stabbed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But just from that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:16.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You regained your memories when you were sleeping on my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:21.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body recognized the sound of its own heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:32.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Yuzuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:38.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you said earlier once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:44.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:52.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:21:01.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me believe what you've always believed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:09.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That living is wonderful!{FOTC; That life is wonderful!}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:17.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be together forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yuzuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:31.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:35.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:44.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for loving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:47.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:48.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:55.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This gift of life you gave me... {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,0:21:58.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:18.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!!
